.TH "ptracer_capable" 9 "ptracer_capable" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
ptracer_capable \- Determine if the ptracer holds CAP_SYS_PTRACE in the namespace
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "bool" ptracer_capable
.BI "(struct task_struct *tsk "  ","
.BI "struct user_namespace *ns "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "tsk" 12
The task that may be ptraced
.IP "ns" 12
The user namespace to search for CAP_SYS_PTRACE in
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Return true if the task that is ptracing the current task had CAP_SYS_PTRACE
in the specified user namespace.
